  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Worn by the homeless and/or junkies. Plastic bags and dirty rags, tattered and stained pants, grimy secondhand shirts and shoes that have seen 3 or 4 owners. Better than being naked, technically, but not by much.</p><p>That said, you can also scrounge it up from pretty much anywhere - finding a free \"outfit\" of this stuff only takes 30 minutes of scrounging on the streets and in dumpsters.</p><p>While worn</p><ul><li><p>You automatically fail <strong>Wardrobe &amp; Style</strong> checks;</p></li><li><p><strong>Personal Grooming</strong> checks are made at a -2;</p></li><li><p>You receive -2 to your <strong>COOL</strong> stat;</p></li><li><p><strong>Wilderness Survival</strong> checks are made at a -2.</p></li><li><p><strong>People will avoid you on the street</strong>, and you likely stink and/or stick to things in at least one way.</p></li></ul>"
    },
